          <history>
            <origin>
              <p>Item is dated 1261 AH and was copied by ʻAlī al-ʻAlawī, a student of al-Ḥājj Muṣṭafá, Khawājah-yi Mashq-i Sarāy-i Humāyūn (f. 18r).</p>
              <origDate>1845</origDate>
              <origPlace>Turkey?</origPlace>
            </origin>
            <provenance>Gift of George Arthur Plimpton, 1936.</provenance>
            <provenance>Formerly owned by George A. Plimpton (bookplate front flyleaf verso).</provenance>
